{"tid":156925,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，我細妹俾人校園欺凌（2）","createTime":"2017-03-15T05:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T08:43:02.000Z","uid":3066,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b107c190bc5f4d4b3d77105e7fb732f91c8d4e27","tid":156925,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我細妹俾人校園欺凌（2）"},{"pid":"66f0629e610c5ad143cb816a06332ae495015c3f","tid":156925,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，我細妹比人校園欺凌。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/151991/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/151991/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>"},{"pid":"357e1f0c386b3726a8eab44f3b2ae0793409830b","tid":156925,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講返件事先，我細妹今年先岩岩讀緊中一。我見佢唔開心左好耐，又無同我講過咩事。我真係好擔心佢。<br />\n<br />\n     終於係前兩日，佢同我講話理上面有個男仔係咁講埋閪啲好負面既說話，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公廁</strong></span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>臭雞</strong></span></span>呢啲好侮辱人嘅說話。<br />\n<br />\n     我自己直頭whatsapp同佢講過，講野唔好咁過份，叫佢收下把口諸如此類既野。佢係有講過對唔住，話唔會再咁樣。但係原來個男仔直頭cap左我同佢既對話放左係我細妹既班群到。又話佢垃圾又盛。<br />\n<br />\n     我真係唔知可以點做，我見到自己細妹日日咁唔開心，我覺得自己做佢呀哥好無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"dfd9857a89b5ef67672d8a214b93c58c82a7cb13","tid":156925,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>hktayy1@yy1.edu.hk<br />\n<br />\n執事先生道鑒：<br />\n<br />\n素聞 貴校致力為本港學生提供優質教育，為本港培育出不少優秀人才。不過，近日 貴校1D班黃嘉輝同學的行為嚴重過失，特致函投訴。<br />\n<br />\n貴校1D班劉女同學在近日長期受到黃同學的言語攻擊及欺凌，在校內外及網絡上指出劉同學為「臭雞」、「公廁」、「妓女」等侮辱性言語攻擊。除此之外，黃同學在校內還多次對劉同學進行人身攻擊及恐嚇，實在令人難以接受，以及令大眾對 貴校的校風、管治方法等有所失望。據聞，劉同學家長早前已與黃同學進行警告，可是黃同學依舊作出以上嚴重行為，跟游說班上同學對劉同學作出侮辱等行為。<br />\n<br />\n現要求 貴校對黃同學進出懲治，要求黃同學向劉同學作出道歉及寫上道歉信，以及承諾劉同學得到合理對待。劉同學曾多次訴出想自殺的念頭，深受黃同學嚴重行為的影響。假若事情未有得到合理處理及惡化，定必保證會報警處理及請求各大媒體介入事情，恐怕令 貴校聲譽有一定影響。<br />\n<br />\n敬祝<br />\n教安<br />\n熱心市民<br />\nX先生<br />\n二零一七年三月十一日</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3917e8c518c6f0ee5bf647ac2662964eb4b16aa3","tid":156925,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/195233_77be3aaada9c2dce3817bad74741d98e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F195233_77be3aaada9c2dce3817bad74741d98e.jpg&h=76e821f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"20eaae54adfd8b1c6953ab27f9be895e97b0c459","tid":156925,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69aca05fe161b9d316dac975f0377df0587edbeb","tid":156925,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/089e959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F089e959.jpg&h=61d39cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ed2c82e57cbc2a7a74478c4fef899bc59f6294c6","tid":156925,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/203849_003a4b0ccadb8ca2b66279a331627a48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F203849_003a4b0ccadb8ca2b66279a331627a48.jpg&h=e2e57963&s={S